{
  "stem": "20800.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All was very heavily [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] armed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had all sort of guns and those rifles and all automatics, all sort of things, and a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they put us in the middle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From one side, the other side, in the front, in the back, SS men was sort of heading us-- that was north Rostock.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We walk a long-- we walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't give us no transportation at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just have to walk wherever we could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I don't even remember having food or water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, no, we had the water, because I-- they give us-- I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't remember at all food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Most probably die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had a feeling that we won't walk long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know because I run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No houses.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say forest, like forest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, it was a road, a big road that-- one side was [? slick ?] down, and further up was little forest with bushes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very small, but not high.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the other side was the same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were walking through the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That much I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they wanted to go quick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schnell, schnell, schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, when you, when you start, you can go schnell, but when you walk a few hours or day, so you can't go schnell.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they-- of course, the, the people who was behind was the hardest time because they could stick you with their gun or whatever they've got and make you [? shoo. ?] A lot of them couldn't make it, so people have to help each other to, to walk.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very bad, very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
